data.name: Label7.Text
data.value:
This is a project that supports a Centralized Registration process which establishes that each student registered or enrolled in the system is uniquely identified on the basis of the Bio-Metric minuature characteristics differences; No other record in the Database represents the same student regardless of how identical the image capture or differences in names or other pieces of information provided by the student are.
The project also encompases a Specialised Sub-System for sending Text Messages (SMS) to parents or guardians after an attendance is taken. This provides a means for them to monitor their children/wards accademic activities (in focus, absence/presence) in the Institution.
